author: Liz Sly
title: Fresh barbs fly between Tehran and Washington over who's to blame for coronavirus's spread in Iran
description: Pompeo accused Iran of lying about the extent of its infections after Khamenei implied the United States may have created the virus.
content:
Secretary of State Mike Pompeo countered on Monday by saying that the fabrications by Khamenei about what Pompeo referred to as the Wuhan Virus put Iranians and people worldwide at risk.
